EFL MOUR OF THE SAME Adrian Durham says Man Utd boss Jose Mourinho remains chained up in his deep, dark football dungeon… it’s like Louis van Gaal never left Old Trafford 
Mourinho needs to move on from his immovable object Zlatan Ibrahimovic and catch up with the rest of modern football Exclusive
